\bustMsgExp[2, 1]\nc<Senpai>It's come again this year. The end-of-year party where we
entertain VIPs and executives.
\nc<Member>Well, you'll understand once we get there.

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>With all the big shots and VIPs gathering... there's no way
it'll be a quiet event like usual.
\bustMsgExp[2, 3]\nc<Senpai>Saki, it's already decided, so brace yourself.

\nc<Employee>The preparations for the end-of-year party have begun.
Members who have been selected, please head to the venue!
